OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774379485
OL,3,CTwelve jailed after investigation into
OL,4,Can illegal Sheffield gun factory
OL,6,FGroup jailed for over 160 years after
OL,7,Finvestigation into the illegal
OL,8,Fconversion of blank firing weapons
OL,9,Finto working guns and ammunition.
OL,11,FThe investigation by South Yorkshire
OL,12,FPolice in Sheffield uncovered one of
OL,13,Fthe UK's largest blank firing weapon
OL,14,Fconversion operations.
OL,16,FIn 2023, over a five-month period, a
OL,17,Fseries of intelligence-led warrants
OL,18,Fled to raids on conversion factory set-
OL,19,Fups in the Darnall, Castlebeck,
OL,20,FRichmond and Beighton areas.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
