FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774379485
OL,3,CTwelve jailed after investigation into
OL,4,Can illegal Sheffield gun factory
OL,6,FThis led to officers recovering
OL,7,Fequipment used by the group to turn
OL,8,Fthe blank firing weapons into deadly
OL,9,Ffirearms.
OL,11,FBetween March and July 2023, officers
OL,12,Frecovered 108 blank firing weapons in
OL,13,Fvarious stages of conversion, as well
OL,14,Fas a significant amount of blank
OL,15,Ffiring ammunition which had been
OL,16,Fconverted into viable ammunition.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
