PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774379485
OL,3,CTwelve jailed after investigation into
OL,4,Can illegal Sheffield gun factory
OL,6,FThrough CCTV trawls, search warrants
OL,7,Fand proactive vehicle stops by
OL,8,Fneighbouring forces, investigators
OL,9,Fdeveloped an in-depth picture of the
OL,10,Fhierarchal structure of the group.
OL,12,FAt earlier hearings, the below men
OL,13,Feither pleaded guilty or were found
OL,14,Fguilty of conspiracy to sell or
OL,15,Ftransfer prohibited weapons and
OL,16,Fconspiracy to manufacture, sell or
OL,17,Ftransfer ammunition.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
