PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774379485
OL,3,CTwelve jailed after investigation into
OL,4,Can illegal Sheffield gun factory
OL,6,FShera Virk, 24, of Golf Lane,
OL,7,FLeamington Spa, and Joseph Steele, 34,
OL,8,Fof Brewery Street, Stratford-upon-
OL,9,FAvon, were both found guilty of three
OL,10,Fcounts of possessing a prohibited
OL,11,Fweapon and one charge of possessing
OL,12,Fammunition.
OL,14,FThey were sentenced at an earlier
OL,15,Fhearing. Virk was sentenced to eight
OL,16,Fyears in prison and Steele was jailed
OL,17,Ffor nine years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
