PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774379485
OL,3,CTwelve jailed after investigation into
OL,4,Can illegal Sheffield gun factory
OL,6,FTemporary Detective Chief Inspector
OL,7,FIain Martin said: "There is no place
OL,8,Ffor the sort of mindless violence gun
OL,9,Fcrime causes in our communities. We
OL,10,Fwill not tolerate gun crime in South
OL,11,FYorkshire.
OL,13,F"This investigation has resulted in a
OL,14,Fsignificant number of weapons seized.
OL,15,FIt is highly likely that these
OL,16,Ffirearms would have got into the hands
OL,17,Fof violent criminals putting innocent
OL,18,Fmembers of the public at risk of harm.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
