PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774379485
OL,3,CTwelve jailed after investigation into
OL,4,Can illegal Sheffield gun factory
OL,6,F"Converted blank firing weapons make
OL,7,Fup a large proportion of firearms
OL,8,Fdischarges in South Yorkshire and this
OL,9,Finvestigation forms part of our
OL,10,Fongoing relentless approach to
OL,11,Ftackling firearm enabled criminality."
OL,13,FAnother person charged in connection
OL,14,Fwith our investigation into the
OL,15,Fconversion of blank firing firearms is
OL,16,Fstill awaiting trial later this year.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
